snippet.title: LumbearJack - Launch Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
LumbearJack is available now on Nintendo Switch: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/lumbearjack-switch/

Grab your axe and save the environment by chopping and recycling every man-made thing in your path and solving puzzles with your charming animal friends!

#LumbearJack #IndieWorld #NintendoSwitch

Subscribe for more Nintendo fun! https://goo.gl/HYYsot
